Casino assigns Jonás Larrazábal, which comes freely
After 72 days of silence the authorized representative of the Casino Red freed the brother of the mayor from Monterrey of the process which is led against it because of probable blackmail.
After 72 days of captivity Manuel Jonás Larrazábal is let to freely after the authorized representative of the Casino Red forgave him before the Second punishment of the district to lead the process against the brother of the mayor from Monterrey because of blackmail.
Sergio Gil García published after the assassination attempt onto the Casino Royale, the owner of the Casino Red, a row of photos and videos on which Manuel Jonás is to be seen that probably forces him for the payment of a sum of money so that the municipal administration approves the secret company of the bet house.
According to the charge the prosecution opened a punishment procedure against the brother of the panistischen mayor who was arrested on the 2nd September for 30 days.
After four hours with the official of the Ministerio Público 3 en Delitos Patrimonial it became brought to the capital into the Casa de Arraigo 1 in the Barrio Antiguo.
At this place it stayed 49 days according to a second warrant of arrest after the official of the Ministerio Público had rejected the crimes because of bribery and organized crime.
On 19th October he was transferred to the custody institution by Cadereyta, because it had bribed probable the owners of the Casino Red with one millions of pesos. On the other hand he remained only a few hours in the central security tract since there were murder threats against it.
The authorities allowed him, at the legal proceedings as an occupant of the urban prison to participate from San Nicolás de los Garza.
On 25th October a custody regulation was delivered to him by the secretary of the Second punishment of the district, Jorge Yánez. This stated that there would be sufficient proofs after the investigations lasting almost two months in order to speak for the payment of 1.5 million pesos to the representatives of the bet house Jonás guiltily in order to be able to open this in the corresponding train.
This Monday the authorized representative of Casino Red requested, Víctor Aldo García Gómez the judge José Luis Pecina, to remit the punishment to the brother of the mayor, for which it is put on free foot in the next hours.
During the judicial hearing Ramiro Arias, the official of the Ministerio Público assigned to the court, García Gómez, asked whether this repaired the damage and which one of the owners of the bet house expressed his pardon. The attorney restrained the name, however.
According to the legal matter 197/2011 Jonás Larrazábal is absolved. Also in the following one no objections to the process can be made, in addition no compensation is demanded.
After the hearing of the authorized representative of the bet house by 15.50 o'clock Larrazabal Bretón was put immediately on free foot.
